                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>According to the Log, <hi rend="italic">ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_843">p.
                        843</ref>, the “household” and McIntire dined together. The “household”
                    presumably included Mrs. Churchill and Subaltern Mary Churchill at least, and
                    may have included other members of the Roosevelt and Churchill parties. No
                    record of the discussion has been found.</p>
            </div>
